<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She is a successful Hollywood actress who rose to prominence for her lead role in teen drama Pretty Little Liars.</p>

<p>And Lucy Hale opted for a laid back look as she went for a hike in Los Angeles on Monday. </p>

<p>The actress, 31, donned a grey T-shirt for the outing along with a pair of pink legging shorts.  </p>

<p>Out and about: Lucy Hale, 31, opted for a laid back look as she went for a hike in Los Angeles on Monday</p>

<p>The TV star also sported a pair of grey trainers and styled her newly dyed red locks into a ponytail while she chatted on the phone.</p>

<p>Wearing a white dove necklace with a multicoloured chain, Lucy also wore a pair of sunglasses for the day.</p>

<p>Carrying a water bottle under her arm, the star appeared to go makeup free for the outing.  </p>

<p>Quarantine inspired Lucy to dig through old family photos and to uncover and share various creations from her youth.</p>

<p>Outfits: The actress donned a grey T-shirt for the outing along with a pair of pink legging shorts</p>

<p>Nostalgic: Aside from working out, quarantine has been inspiring Lucy to dig through old family photos and various creations from her youth</p>

<p>Most recently, the actress showed off a headshot she had taken when she was just 10-years-old.</p>

<p>The actress compared her younger self to her current self on her Instagram Story as she held the headshot up to her face.</p>

<p>Lucy portrayed title character Katy Keene in The CW spin-off of Riverdale that premiered in February, but the series was canceled in July after one season.</p>

<p>Lucy had a starring role in the Fantasy Island supernatural horror film that was released on February 14 in theatres.</p>

<p>The prequel to the 1977 ABC television series earned $48million worldwide against a production budget of $7million.</p>

<p>Star: Lucy rose to prominence for her lead role in teen drama Pretty Little Liars</p>
